{"tid":1467081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【 緊 急 】三 招 輕 鬆 對 付 有 鬼！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:43:41.000Z","uid":124932,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"61fe2e7dd9fa344fbc4fb3b979b8c14a6183c5ad","tid":1467081,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:10.000Z","msg":"方法 / 原因如下<br />\n<br />\n一。幫手塞就唔係鬼，分隔嘈緊既人，繼續目標&minus; 癱瘓機場，<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔係鬼既都會大局為重</span><br />\n<br />\n二。鬼既責任係搗亂，佢嘈第一次就已經引起注意，<span style=\"color: gold;\">只要唔捉鬼，佢就任務失敗</span>，再搗亂，其他人就知又係佢<br />\n<br />\n三。你係機場，唔係出面，<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔會有狗推進</span>，所以唔會有鬼係狗推進時跳岀來撲低你<br />\n<br />\n狗可以扮鬼，又可以扮捉鬼，你要做既係<span style=\"color: gold;\">冷處理，分隔佢地</span><br />\n<br />\n一句講哂<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鬼係捉唔哂，大局為重，癱瘓機場</span></span>"},{"pid":"edaf08e5f1b00b7779071e12d95bcdfce3688a10","tid":1467081,"uid":124932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:07.000Z","msg":"同意既幫推"},{"pid":"a37657452f079fb8694e6a8c05a1419f7f6031cb","tid":1467081,"uid":22632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92479d34ea79a13261bf3bd68759e00f1e9153a1","tid":1467081,"uid":217607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:03.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2c08abc22f80e504a6b05ea223502686f0355d5f","tid":1467081,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:18.000Z","msg":"鬼係捉唔哂，大局為重，癱瘓機場"},{"pid":"77d3ec9e9334c906ea89b34ac68336bfceadf553","tid":1467081,"uid":13308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:18.000Z","msg":"幫推, 要冷靜處事"},{"pid":"7cfded1be544872d90133e37a0dcb57e3bf51e88","tid":1467081,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:07.000Z","msg":"鬼係捉唔哂，大局為重，癱瘓機場<br />\n<br />\n不分化，全部人目標一致呀！"},{"pid":"00d75efd9d9cc318a0014826b