"},{"pid":"3e97aa4608ef71c283d0672f0c9dae7f298403e6","tid":1467081,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:22.000Z","msg":"黑警博清場，所有野都係黑警UC安排既，我堅持呢一點，我唔理，總之黑警&amp;公安混入示威者就係唔岩<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼，簡單方法，給個印落佢額頭度，或寫個鬼在當眼位，唔好咁易洗得甩，之後放佢走<br />\n<br />\n如何處理發現到既鬼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466303</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d62415f071808ff0b499e40aff9aff0c9706de82","tid":1467081,"uid":128883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77d3ec9e9334c906ea89b34ac68336bfceadf553","tid":1467081,"uid":13308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:18.000Z","msg":"幫推, 要冷靜處事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c11bbd5940e15dbe818808f1301364f22f90afcf","tid":1467081,"uid":77170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d17f92eb11c459478b1909de4ce51e607df575","tid":1467081,"uid":126309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:50.000Z","msg":"有巴打講過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆就撕一貼百<br />\n對家內鬼就捉一滲百</span><br />\n捉鬼只會沒完沒了，仲會弱我軍心<br />\n大家只需提醒同路人提防就夠<br />\n<br />\n返回最初0805、0811發現有鬼果句<br />\n<strong>小隊行動，小心行事</strong><br />\n<br />\n再套用天琦果句 唔好被仇恨支配，保持冷靜理性"},{"pid":"78417707c6b6218fea039712e8a028851ac8a4fd","tid":1467081,"uid":261743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"61fe2e7dd9fa344fbc4fb3b979b8c14a6183c5ad","tid":1467081,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:10.000Z","msg":"方法 / 原因如下<br />\n<br />\n一。幫手塞就唔係鬼，分隔嘈緊既人，繼續目標&minus; 癱瘓機場，<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔係鬼既都會大局為重</span><br />\n<br />\n二。鬼既責任係搗亂，佢嘈第一次就已經引起注意，<span style=\"color: gold;\">只要唔捉鬼，佢就任務失敗</span>，再搗亂，其他人就知又係佢<br />\n<br />\n三。你係機場，唔係出面，<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔會有狗推進</span>，所以唔會有鬼係狗推進時跳岀來撲低你<br />\n<br />\n狗可以扮鬼，又可以扮捉鬼，你要做既係<span style=\"color: gold;\">冷處理，分隔佢地</span><br />\n<br />\n一句講哂<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鬼係捉唔哂，大局為重，癱瘓機場</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n要捉鬼，又要好睇<br />\n影出黎正面而有說服力<br />\n最好嘅方法，係叫記者去捉<br />\n<br />\n例如第一次喺cwb，tvb記者追問個垃圾係唔係狗，成件事已經令警察單位無任何說服力<br />\n<br />\n我地手足圍鬼，就一定有&quot;人&quot; 會打鬼<br />\n只要唔比佢走，叫記者過黎<br />\n1.說話盤問技巧比我地好<br />\n2.大大個cam影住佢點答都係死<br />\n3.夠正面，夠公道<br />\n4.只要比所有人知入面係有鬼，自然就無人再信警察單位<br />\n<br />\n簡單講之後做乜都可以，因為根本就係警察滲透到各層面而令暴力不斷出現。<br />\n佢呢一步好毒，但因爲太毒，同時風險都太高<br />\n因而有太多野比我地去反利用，要珍惜<br />\n<br />\nMedia時代，用media去解決問題<br />\n用media去令對方不斷失敗<br />\n任何外力，都可以係助力"},{"pid":"2c4cc48e639c39b059d5d2b7bbe5f55d7206777b","tid":1467081,"uid":268860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:19.000Z","msg":"岩 對準目標"},{"pid":"be698069ded019c549730ee3310f8e794a917010","tid":1467081,"uid":32387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:21.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"2dfe57fe1535b5a01f14a0c03c58d60178ff4b85","tid":1467081,"uid":290697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:29.000Z","msg":"鬼捉唔哂"},{"pid":"8161d67fc15fe2cdde1ecd9c0be2563547077ac3","tid":1467081,"uid":271777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:37.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"20626b840efc4e635605b111e847407f8587bccf","tid":1467081,"uid":232921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:42.000Z","msg":"對抗緊共匪，不是玩，要冷靜！冷靜"},{"pid":"701842c13c7977e5c5801da9a1e24692ffe41438","tid":1467081,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:05.000Z","msg":"大局為重"},{"pid":"5559da8adaa1f708b9c409b95ab07720e5f6ae01","tid":1467081,"uid":271777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:24.000Z","msg":"推啊😭"},{"pid":"56559a02330f964d94b029d767900838de5b016d","tid":1467081,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:46.000Z","msg":"得罪講句 喺機場入面有鬼都冇所謂 佢做唔到d乜<br />\n反而要多謝佢幫手塞人<br />\n千其唔好因爲捉鬼而失去理智<br />\n大家要保留清晰頭腦<br />\n比人鬧可能會好嬲 但都請可以冷靜一秒諗一諗先"},{"pid":"3e900480f8be5a1a4b39369c3a0ccb54e833e9a1","tid":1467081,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:31.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 和理飛814<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466833</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5544f80f1caf081945c4392018f9b7227d758342","tid":1467081,"uid":265152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:15:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e28ae33161e4df14de06be4806eaa216d5e0b77","tid":1467081,"uid":133100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86d59c42209953284d66e1fc2e13118726cdd2b","tid":1467081,"uid":133100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ab99fde066a67162ead6297862c3f3f7ba06fc","tid":1467081,"uid":133100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:55.000Z","msg":"我地示威者<br />\n「唔完美，可接受，但需要改善、改進。」<br />\n1. 不打記者<br />\n2. 不打救護<br />\n3. 不濫用酷刑<br />\n4. 不攻擊平民"},{"pid":"522b2a25b48f78438acd8319380b2fe562814248","tid":1467081,"uid":203619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:06.000Z","msg":"我只推 正常POST<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/RfNfTgW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfNfTgW.png&h=52691539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日我留意到最大單係警察係機場用槍指嚇市民<br />\n你地又留意到咩呢?<br />\n希望大家理性啲 幫手推返正常POST"},{"pid":"8